      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can you go a bit deeper into the economic and legal arguments? like, specifically regarding the strain on local infrastructure and the principle of the rule of law. my students need to be able to articulate the specific philosophical and practical logic behind these points, not just the general idea.",
